ZOSUIUserCredentialsManager - Class in com.compuware.api.topaz.eclipse.hostcredentials.zos
This manager is used to connect a Topaz Workbench UI user to a z/OS host configured in the Topaz Workbench client and to retrieve their credentials for connecting to a z/OS host with the Topaz API.
